\c 2
\s Kuberekwa kwaJesu Kristu
\p
\v 1 Zvino namazuva iwayo, chirevo chakaitwa naKesari Augusto, kuti nyika yose inyorwe mazita.
\v 2 Uku ndokwaiva kunyorwa kokutanga kwakaitwa Kuriniosi ari mubati weSiria.
\v 3 Vanhu vose vakaenda kundonyorwa, mumwe nomumwe kuguta rake.
\v 4 NaJosefavo wakabva Gariri, muguta reNazareta, akaenda Judhiya, kuguta raDhavhidhi, rinonzi Bhetirehemu, nokuti waiva weimba yaDhavhidhi, noworudzi rwaDhavhidhi;
\v 5 kuti anyorwe naMaria, wakanga atsidzira kuwanikwa naye, ava nemimba.
\v 6 Zvakaitika kuti vachipo, mazuva okuzvara kwake akasvika;
\v 7 akazvara mwanakomana wake wedangwe, akamuputira nemicheka, akamuvanzarika muchidyiro chezvipfuwo, nokuti makanga musina nzvimbo muimba yavaeni.
\s Vafudzi veBhetirehemu
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakanga kunavafudzi munyika iyo, vaigara kuvuragu vachirinda mapoka avo vusiku.
\v 9 Zvino tarira mutumwa waShe akamira pedo navo, nokubwinya kwaShe kukaratidzwa kwakavakomba, vakatya nokutya kukuru.
\v 10 Ipapo mutumwa akati kwavari: Musatya; nokuti tarira, ndinokuparidzirai mashoko omufaro mukuru, uchava wavanhu vose;
\v 11 nokuti mazvarirwa nhasi muguta raDhavhidhi Muponesi, ndiye Kristu Ishe.
\v 12 Ichi chiratidzo kwamuri: Muchandowana rusvava rwakaputirwa nemicheka, ruvete muchidyiro chezvipfuwo.
\v 13 Ipapo kamwe-kamwe kukavapo pamwe chete nomutumwa, gurumwandira rehondo yokudenga, richirumbidza Mwari, richiti:
\v 14 Rumbidzo kunaMwari wokumusoro-soro, rugare ruve panyika, nomoyo muchena kuvanhu.
\v 15 Zvino kwakati vatumwa vabva kwavari, vaenda kudenga, vafudzi vakataurirana, vachiti: Ngatiende hedu Bhetirehemu, tindovona chinhu ichi chakaitwa, chatakaziviswa naShe.
\v 16 Ipapo vakakurumidza kusvika, vakawana vose Maria naJosefa, norushiye ruvete muchidyiro chezvipfuwo.
\v 17 Vakati vavona, vakazivisa kose shoko ravakanga vavudzwa maererano nomwana uyo.
\v 18 Vose vakanzwa vakashamiswa nezvinhu izvi zvavakavudzwa navafudzi.
\v 19 Asi Maria wakachengeta mashoko iwayo ose, achifungisisa mumoyo make.
\v 20 Zvino vafudzi vakadzokera kwakare, vachikudza nokurumbidza Mwari pamusoro pezvose zvavakanzwa nezvavakavona, sezvavakanga vavudzwa.
\s Jesu unoiswa mutembere, Simiyoni naAna
\p
\v 21 Mazuva masere akati apera, kuti adzingiswe, vakatumidza zita rake Jesu, iro raakanga atumidzwa nomutumwa, asati agamuchirwa mudumbu.
\v 22 Zvino mazuva okuzvinatsa kwavo nomurairo waMozisi akati apera, vakavuya naye Jerusarema, kuti vamuise pamberi paShe;
\v 23 (sezvazvakanyorwa pamurairo waShe, zvichinzi: Mwanarume mumwe nomumwe unotanga kuzarura chizvaro, uchanzi mutsvene kunaShe),
\v 24 vuye kubayira chibayiro; sezvazvakarebwa pamurairo waShe, njiva mbiri, kana hangaiwa mbiri duku.
\v 25 Zvino tarira, kwakanga kunomunhu, paJerusarema, wainzi Simiyoni; waiva munhu wakarurama waida Mwari waimirira kunyaradzwa kwavaIsraeri, noMweya Mutsvene wakanga anaye.
\v 26 Iye wakanga aratidzwa noMweya Mutsvene, kuti haangavoni rufu, asati avona Kristu waShe.
\v 27 Wakavuya mutembere noMweya; zvino vabereki vakati vachivuya nomwana Jesu, kuti vaite naye nomutovo womurairo,
\v 28 akamutora, akamubata mumavoko ake akarumbidza Mwari, achiti:
\v 29 Tenzi zvino regai muranda wenyu aende norugare sezvamakareva;
\p
\v 30 Nokuti meso angu avona ruponeso rwenyu,
\v 31 rwamakagadzirira pamberi pezviso zvavanhu vose
\v 32 Chiedza chokuvhenekera vahedheni, nokurumbidzwa kwavanhu venyu vaIsraeri.
\v 33 Josefa namai vake vakashamiswa nezvakarebwa pamusoro pake.
\v 34 Ipapo Simiyoni akavaropafadza, akati kunaMaria, mai vake: Tarira, uyu wakaisirwa kuwa nokumuka kwavazhinji pavaIsraeri. Chichava chiratidzo chichapikiswa;
\v 35 vuye munondo uchabaya mweya wakovo; kuti ndangariro dzemoyo mizhinji dziiswe pachena.
\v 36 Zvino kwakanga kunaAnavo muporofitakadzi, mukunda waFanueri, worudzi rwaAsheri; (iye wakanga akwegura kwazvo, wakanga anomurume makore manomwe kubvira pavumhandara bwake.
\v 37 wakanga ari chirikadzi yaiva namakore makumi masere namana), wakanga asingabvi mutembere, achishumira Mwari nokutsanya nokunyengetera vusiku namasikati:
\v 38 Naiye wakati achisvika nenguva iyo, akatendavo Mwari, akataura pamusoro pake kunavose vakanga vachitarira kusunungurwa kweJerusarema.
\v 39 Zvino vakati vapedza zvinhu zvose zvomurairo waShe, vakadzokera Gariri, kuguta ravo Nazareta.
\v 40 Mwana akakura, akava nesimba mumweya akazara nenjere; nenyasha dzaMwari dzikava pamusoro pake.
\s Jesu pakati pavadzidzisi vakuru.
\p
\v 41 Zvino vabereki vake vaisienda Jerusarema makore ose kumutambo wepaseka.
\v 42 Zvino iye wakati ava namakore anegumi namaviri, vakaenda Jerusarema netsika yomutambo.
\v 43 Vakati vapedza mazuva, pakudzoka kwavo mwana Jesu akasara Jerusarema, Josefa namai vake vasingazvizivi.
\v 44 Asi zvavaiti zvimwe uri kunavamwe vakanga vari panzira navo, vakafamba zuva rimwe, vakazomutsvaka kuhama dzavo nokuvazikani vavo.
\v 45 Vakati vamushaiwa, vakadzokera Jerusarema vachimutsvaka.
\v 46 Mazuva matatu; akati apfuvura, vakamuwana ari mutembere, agere pakati pavadzidzisi achivateerera nokuvabvunza.
\v 47 Vose vakanga vachimunzwa, vakashamiswa nokuziva kwake vuye nokupindura kwake.
\v 48 Zvino vakati vamuvona, vakakatyamara; mai vake vakati kwaari: Mwana, waitireiko zvakadai? Tarira, baba vako neni takutsvaka tichichema.
\v 49 Akati kwavari: Makanga muchinditsvakireiko? Makanga musingazivi kuti ndinofanira kuva pazvinhu zvaBaba vangu here?
\v 50 Vakasanzwisisa shoko raakavavudza.
\v 51 Ipapo akaburuka navo, akasvika Nazareta, akavateerera. Mai vake vakachengeta mashoko iwayo ose mumoyo mavo.
\v 52 Jesu akaramba achienda mberi pakuchenjera napakukura, napakufadza Mwari navanhu.
